  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a bowl, whisk almond flour, coconut flour, and sea salt together.",
    "Add warm coconut oil and egg, mix until dough forms.",
    "Chill dough in the fridge for 10 minutes.",
    "Roll dough into a circle and fit into a 9-inch tart pan.",
    "Spread blueberries evenly over the crust.",
    "Sprinkle lemon zest and orange zest over the berries.",
    "Drizzle lemon juice over the fruit.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes until crust is golden and berries burst.",
    "Remove from oven, let cool 5 minutes, then serve warm."
